  "title": "Security Officer ( CNY PACKAGE ) 16-20 Feb 2026",
  "description": "<p><strong>Reachfield Security (Grade “A” agency) specializes in supplying security manpower to Schools, Factories, Shopping Centres, Museums, libraries, etc.</strong><br /></p><p>Security Officer (CNY Package)</p><p><strong>Location: North/Central/East </strong></p><p><strong>Salary: Gross up to $175 per day </strong><br /></p><p>1. Works in a school/ office building environment.</p><p>2. Good customer service skills; able to communicate with people of all levels.</p><p>3. 12hrs-shift (Fixed shift, no need to rotate)</p><p>4. PC knowledge required.</p><p>5. Job duties include traffic control, issue visitors/ contractor passes, patrolling, protecting clients’ premises and access control, etc.</p><p>6. Possess valid security license, completed WSQ RTT.<br /><br /><strong>Office:10 Anson Road, #26-09 International Plaza</strong></p><p><strong>(Near Tanjong Pagar MRT Exit C)</strong></p><p><strong>Contact Us</strong></p><p><u><strong>Mobile: 9137 4851 Office: 6324 0648 ( Janet )</strong></u></p><p>You may fill in the application form online thru below link.</p><p>https://rss.armfort.com/direct... </p><p>Do let us know once you submit the application online</p>",
